rows.label: tlk45320292_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I thought I wanted to get out
of here and back to Superbia
as soon as possible...

rows.label: tlk45320292_02_msg0002
rows.name:
But right now, with everywhere in
the middle of conflict, it might
actually be safer to stay here.

rows.label: tlk45320292_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I just hope my mum back home's all
right. D'you think she followed
my advice and fled to Gula...?
